{"title":"CVE-2009-3895","uid":"2b8027731040e609d5e8b6f6157502a6","slug":"[Fuzzing Lab] Exercise 2 - libexif","date":"2023-04-12T14:18:00.000Z","updated":"2024-03-13T00:55:13.872Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/[Fuzzing Lab] Exercise 2 - libexif.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>Today we reproduce CVE-2009-3895.</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p>We have produce the seed we need to figure out why make it core dumped with AFL++.<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FlhM4hduqDrcLQ9UUuEmiVu66KYj.png\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/antonio-morales/Fuzzing101/issues/11\">https://github.com/antonio-morales/Fuzzing101/issues/11</a><br>The makefile iusses I find…</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/nbu_dahe/article/details/122105306\">gdb-reverse debug</a><br>Now we need to re-complie it with default compiler, and use gdb to find what the problem in it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FjQjacWMBDBinYoj7Q-HAapHrrsh.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FtFVxAO0adZkThvcXDLJO-_z6LSs.png\"></p>\n<p>Collapse chain is <code>main</code> -&gt; <code>exif_loader_get_data</code> -&gt; <code>exif_data_load_data</code> -&gt; <code>exif_get_short</code> -&gt; <code>exif_get_sshort</code></p>\n<p>d+6+offset is unaccessable memory address, so when rip run it will error!<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FnKyZR6NUbr-Jn3li3Wd_MWnNZvQ.png\"><br>We should figure out what is d and offset!</p>\n<p>buf&#x3D;0x55565558c8e3 &lt;error: Cannot access memory at address 0x55565558c8e3&gt;<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FiRNhZSdK2jKmEjOiPFkZNU7on3P.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FuIXWSEuy5ogbOE-YroHQW1oLB_v.png\"></p>\n<p>The big problem we found is this offset!<br>Normal offset is 0x8<br>Malicious offset is 0xfffffffd</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\">offset <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">exif_get_long</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> data<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>priv<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>order<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Normal<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FiPf0rYR_-FltvsLrQKVMbmNPkJ7.png\"></p>\n<p>The crash jpg<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fp_4J833Gfx166NQheMH0Q7EplgL.png\"></p>\n<p>We can found <code>00000020</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">00 2a ff ff ff fd\n\n45 78 69 66 ----&gt; Exif\nff ff ff fd ----&gt; b+10<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FshOrttmtC9lIxsRktCssoNdA_UL.png\"></p>\n<p>Normal<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fo-_oQNehk942td9rC7B54AmHfkv.png\"></p>\n<p>It will return 0xfffffffd and make p+6+offset unacessable.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/Fh1ofRMDvqqZXaajJ1M21J_I0khc.png\"></p>\n<p>So we fix the bug in rudeness…<br><img src=\"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/FuhImsXfOwq3HuRJt3tq14ex42Ea.png\"></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"Today we reproduce CVE-2009-3895. We have produce the seed we need to figure out why make it core dumped with AFL++. https://github.com/anto...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":997,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Fuzzing","slug":"Fuzzing","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Fuzzing.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"TinMan","slug":"TinMan","count":3,"path":"api/tags/TinMan.json"},{"name":"CVE Re-discovery","slug":"CVE-Re-discovery","count":2,"path":"api/tags/CVE-Re-discovery.json"},{"name":"Fuzzing Lab","slug":"Fuzzing-Lab","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Fuzzing-Lab.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Leviathan","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"Cybersec student","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Simple Smart Contract Development","uid":"0e057c8e76400e897cc2b47c2a4540db","slug":"[Block Chain] Smart Contract Developmen","date":"2024-03-02T14:18:00.000Z","updated":"2024-03-13T00:55:09.588Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/[Block Chain] Smart Contract Developmen.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":" 代理投票需求实现一个带有代理功能的投票智能合约。 思路 定义投票者 Voter 的结构体，定义提案 Proposal 的结构体。 Voter 可以对 Proposal 进行投票，同时 VoterA 可以把自己的代理权给 VoterB，但是必须可以追踪到。例如 A-&gt;B-&...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.8k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"SmartContract","slug":"SmartContract","count":1,"path":"api/categories/SmartContract.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"BlockChain","slug":"BlockChain","count":1,"path":"api/tags/BlockChain.json"},{"name":"Smart-Contract","slug":"Smart-Contract","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Smart-Contract.json"}],"author":{"name":"Leviathan","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://l3vi4th4n.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/blog-images/avatar.jpg","link":"/","description":"Cybersec student","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{"title":"CVE-2019-13288 ","uid":"f3ecffc809bb940d1b